(27, 1, '2022-09-08 09:19:20', '2022-09-08 09:19:20', '<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":1} -->\n<h1 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center">The Minecraft Server</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->\n<p class="has-text-align-center"><strong><a href="http://map.taeko-and-co.ch:3876" data-type="link" data-id="http://map.taeko-and-co.ch:3876" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Link to server map</a> (BlueMap)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The server is the original, and logically the longest ongoing, Taeko &amp; Co project. It is a large world (around 40 GB) with many different regions, cities and builds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>In one sentence, I\'d say that Taeko &amp; Co. is a server that focuses on developing not only realistic cities, but entire countries, with all the towns, farms and infrastructure in between, in the confines of semi-vanilla Minecraft.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Goal/Objective of the Server</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The general goal (if you can really even call it a "goal") is to realistically build fictive countries inside of Minecraft, while still respecting vanilla terrain (although terraforming and such is not taboo, of course). Professional tools such as AutoCAD and Adobe Illustrator are used for planning and drafting future developments. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading">The World Itself</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Taeko &amp; Co uses the <strong>Create mod</strong> as well as certain Create extensions, but does not use any other content or gameplay mods, as the goal is to remain <strong>as faithful to Minecraft\'s vanilla style as possible</strong>. The world is entirely seed generated. Since 2020 and version 1.15.2, the server has been updated to every significant version up to 1.20.1. The biome generation preset was also switched to large biomes for version 1.18.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The folder size of the world is about 40 GB.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Political Structure of the Server</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The structure of the server is territorial. Each player decides whether or not they want to have their own country, or be part of another. Inside of your country, you are free to build constructively as you wish, in whatever style you like. However, a lot of importance is placed on serverwide infrastructure, like roads and rail. It is for this reason that at least a basic level of international infrastructure is, de facto, required. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are now happily excepting anyone who is interested in what we do to join the server and build along with us:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"constrained"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:gutena/forms {"formID":"gutena_forms_ID_983bc5fe4a_305202394615","formName":"Application Form","formClasses":"gutena-forms-application-form gutena_forms_ID_983bc5fe4a_305202394615 after_submit_message","adminEmails":"admin@taeko.ch","adminEmailSubject":"Application Taeko \\u0026 Co","formStyle":" .gutena-forms-application-form {\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dplaceholder-color:#808080;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dinput-bg-color:transparent;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dlabel-font-size:1rem;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dlabel-line-height:;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dlabel-font-weight:400;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dplaceholder-font-size:13px;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dplaceholder-line-height:;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dplaceholder-font-weight:400;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dinput-border-width:1px;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dgutena-forms\\u002d\\u002dinput-border-radius:0px;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dstyle\\u002d\\u002dblock-gap:2rem;\\n\\t\\t\\t}\\n\\n\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t.editor-styles-wrapper .gutena-forms-application-form \\u003e .block-editor-inner-blocks \\u003e .block-editor-block-list__layout \\u003e * + * {\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tmargin-block-start: 2rem;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tmargin-block-end: 0;\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t}\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\n\\n\\t\\t\\t .gutena-forms-application-form .wp-block-gutena-field-group {\\u002d\\u002dwp\\u002d\\u002dstyle\\u002d\\u002dblock-gap:10px;}\\n\\t\\t\\t","recaptcha":{"enable":true,"type":"v3","site_key":"6Lco-k8mAAAAAMl1k_8wOVTwHyHV1zPwfX1Xz6et","secret_key":"6Lco-k8mAAAAACfzEsuYL4SuyZsZB1B6yj6CeAOW","thresholdScore":"0.50"},"style":{"spacing":{"blockGap":"2rem","padding":{"top":"2rem","bottom":"5rem"}}}} -->\n<form method="post" class="wp-block-gutena-forms gutena-forms-application-form gutena_forms_ID_983bc5fe4a_305202394615 after_submit_message" style="padding-top:2rem;padding-bottom:5rem"><input type="hidden" name="formid" value="gutena_forms_ID_983bc5fe4a_305202394615"/><!-- wp:gutena/field-group {"fieldLabel":"Field label","fieldLabelContent":"First name","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Enter your first name"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-gutena-field-group"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","className":"gutena-field-group-row"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"placeholder":"Field label","className":"heading-input-label-gutena"} -->\n<h3 class="wp-block-heading heading-input-label-gutena">First name / Online name</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/form-field {"nameAttr":"first_name","fieldName":"First name / Online name","fieldClasses":"gutena-forms-field text-field required-field","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Enter your first name","textAreaRows":2} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"gutena-forms-field-error-msg"} -->\n<p class="gutena-forms-field-error-msg"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:gutena/field-group -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/field-group {"fieldLabel":"Field label","fieldLabelContent":"Last name","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Enter your last name"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-gutena-field-group"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","className":"gutena-field-group-row"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"placeholder":"Field label","className":"heading-input-label-gutena"} -->\n<h3 class="wp-block-heading heading-input-label-gutena">Minecraft Username</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/form-field {"nameAttr":"last_name","fieldName":"Minecraft Username","fieldClasses":"gutena-forms-field text-field required-field","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Enter your last name","textAreaRows":2} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"gutena-forms-field-error-msg"} -->\n<p class="gutena-forms-field-error-msg"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:gutena/field-group -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/field-group {"fieldLabel":"Field label","fieldLabelContent":"Email","fieldType":"email","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"example@gmail.com"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-gutena-field-group"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","className":"gutena-field-group-row"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"placeholder":"Field label","className":"heading-input-label-gutena"} -->\n<h3 class="wp-block-heading heading-input-label-gutena">Email</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/form-field {"nameAttr":"email","fieldName":"Email","fieldClasses":"gutena-forms-field email-field required-field","fieldType":"email","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"example@gmail.com","textAreaRows":2} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"gutena-forms-field-error-msg"} -->\n<p class="gutena-forms-field-error-msg"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:gutena/field-group -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/field-group {"fieldLabel":"Field label","fieldLabelContent":"Subject","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Subject"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-gutena-field-group"><!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"gutena-forms-field-error-msg"} -->\n<p class="gutena-forms-field-error-msg"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:gutena/field-group -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/field-group {"fieldLabel":"Field label","fieldLabelContent":"Message","fieldType":"textarea","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Type here","textAreaRows":5} -->\n<div class="wp-block-gutena-field-group"><!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical","className":"gutena-field-group-row"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"placeholder":"Field label","className":"heading-input-label-gutena"} -->\n<h3 class="wp-block-heading heading-input-label-gutena">Motivation for joining the server (feel free to include previous experience)</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/form-field {"nameAttr":"message","fieldName":"Motivation for joining the server (feel free to include previous experience)","fieldClasses":"gutena-forms-field textarea-field required-field","fieldType":"textarea","isRequired":true,"placeholder":"Type here"} /--></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"gutena-forms-field-error-msg"} -->\n<p class="gutena-forms-field-error-msg"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:gutena/field-group -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {"className":"gutena-forms-submit-buttons"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-buttons gutena-forms-submit-buttons"><!-- wp:button {"placeholder":"Submit","className":"gutena-forms-submit-button"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-button gutena-forms-submit-button"><a class="wp-block-button__link wp-element-button">Submit</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/form-confirm-msg -->\n<div class="wp-block-gutena-form-confirm-msg"><!-- wp:group {"style":{"spacing":{"blockGap":"8px","padding":{"bottom":"12px","right":"12px","left":"12px","top":"12px"}},"color":{"background":"#d8eacc"},"border":{"radius":"5px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"left"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="border-radius:5px;background-color:#d8eacc;padding-top:12px;padding-right:12px;padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:12px"><!-- wp:image {"id":3811,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none","className":"form-message-icon"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large form-message-icon"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Success" class="wp-image-3811"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.2","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"500","fontSize":"12px"}},"textColor":"black","fontSize":"tiny"} -->\n<p class="has-black-color has-text-color has-tiny-font-size" style="font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;line-height:1.2">Your request has been submitted successfully!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:gutena/form-confirm-msg -->\n\n<!-- wp:gutena/form-error-msg -->\n<div class="wp-block-gutena-form-error-msg"><!-- wp:group {"style":{"spacing":{"blockGap":"8px","padding":{"bottom":"12px","right":"12px","left":"12px","top":"12px"}},"color":{"background":"#ffd3d3"},"border":{"radius":"5px"}},"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap","verticalAlignment":"center","justifyContent":"left"}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-group has-background" style="border-radius:5px;background-color:#ffd3d3;padding-top:12px;padding-right:12px;padding-bottom:12px;padding-left:12px"><!-- wp:image {"id":3811,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none","className":"form-message-icon"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large form-message-icon"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Error" class="wp-image-3811"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"gutena-forms-error-text","style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"1.2","fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"500","fontSize":"12px"}},"textColor":"black"} -->\n<p class="gutena-forms-error-text has-black-color has-text-color" style="font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:500;line-height:1.2">Sorry! your request could not be submitted, Please check the errors above. Ensure you have filled all the required fields.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:gutena/form-error-msg --></form>\n<!-- /wp:gutena/forms --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":356,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/1-1024x551.png" alt="" class="wp-image-356"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->\n<p class="has-text-align-center"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->\n<p class="has-text-align-center"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center"} -->\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center">Custom Mod Downloads</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All mods download as .zip archives and not .jar archives! This is due to limitations of the website platform. Please first decompress the download before putting the file in your mods folder.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:file {"id":354,"href":"https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TCSeasonsMod-1.1.0.jar_.zip"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-file"><a id="wp-block-file--media-e3c714aa-ae27-4201-9ead-39943b45bbad" href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TCSeasonsMod-1.1.0.jar_.zip">TCSeasonsMod-1.1.0.jar_</a><a href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TCSeasonsMod-1.1.0.jar_.zip" class="wp-block-file__button wp-element-button" download aria-describedby="wp-block-file--media-e3c714aa-ae27-4201-9ead-39943b45bbad">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The TCSeasons mod adds seasons to Minecraft in a simple way. The client mod is not required, but enhances the experience. It is used on the T&amp;C server. Learn more. <a href="https://github.com/taeko-chan/TCSeasonsMod">Source.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {"id":353,"href":"https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TCBoatTweaker-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar_.zip"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-file"><a id="wp-block-file--media-f7e97a64-6230-483e-84a8-52e2c13bd534" href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TCBoatTweaker-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar_.zip">TCBoatTweaker-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar_</a><a href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TCBoatTweaker-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar_.zip" class="wp-block-file__button wp-element-button" download aria-describedby="wp-block-file--media-f7e97a64-6230-483e-84a8-52e2c13bd534">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The TCBoatTweaker Ultra mod enables boats to go up packed &amp; blue ice blocks. Client side only, may trigger anticheat! Learn more. <a href="https://github.com/taeko-chan/TCBoatTweaker-Ultra">Source.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center"} -->\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center">List of Posts</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:query {"queryId":43,"query":{"perPage":3,"pages":0,"offset":0,"postType":"post","order":"desc","orderBy":"date","author":"","search":"","exclude":[],"sticky":"","inherit":false,"taxQuery":{"category":[13,14]}}} -->\n<div class="wp-block-query"><!-- wp:post-template {"layout":{"type":"grid","columnCount":3}} -->\n<!-- wp:post-title {"isLink":true} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:post-featured-image {"isLink":true,"align":"wide"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:post-excerpt /-->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {"opacity":"css"} -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-css-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:post-date /-->\n<!-- /wp:post-template --></div>\n<!-- /wp:query -->', 'Minecraft Server', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'minecraft-server', '', '', '2025-03-18 15:38:22', '2025-03-18 14:38:22', '', 0, 'https://taeko-and-co.ch/?page_id=27', 0, 'page', '', 0),
