(120, 1, '2022-09-27 12:08:10', '2022-09-27 12:08:10', '<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":1} -->\n<h1 class="has-text-align-center">The Minecraft Server</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The server is the original, and logically the longest ongoing, Taeko &amp; Co project. It is a large world (10GB+) with many different regions, cities and builds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->\n<p class="has-text-align-center"><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="http://server.taeko-and-co.ch:8100" target="_blank">Server Map</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {"height":"40px"} -->\n<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center"} -->\n<h2 class="has-text-align-center">Custom Mod Downloads</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:file {"id":117,"href":"https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/TCWeatherMod-1.0.0.jar_.zip","align":"center"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-file aligncenter"><a id="wp-block-file--media-e3c714aa-ae27-4201-9ead-39943b45bbad" href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/TCWeatherMod-1.0.0.jar_.zip">TCWeatherMod-1.0.0.jar_</a><a href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/TCWeatherMod-1.0.0.jar_.zip" class="wp-block-file__button" download aria-describedby="wp-block-file--media-e3c714aa-ae27-4201-9ead-39943b45bbad">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The TCSeasons mod adds seasons to Minecraft in a simple way. The client mod is not required, but enhances the experience. It is used on the T&amp;C server.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {"id":119,"href":"https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/TCBoatTweakerUltra.jar_.zip"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-file"><a id="wp-block-file--media-f7e97a64-6230-483e-84a8-52e2c13bd534" href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/TCBoatTweakerUltra.jar_.zip">TCBoatTweakerUltra.jar_</a><a href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/TCBoatTweakerUltra.jar_.zip" class="wp-block-file__button" download aria-describedby="wp-block-file--media-f7e97a64-6230-483e-84a8-52e2c13bd534">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The TCBoatTweakerUltra mod enables boats to go up packed &amp; blue ice blocks. Client side only, may trigger anticheat!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Minecraft Server', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-09-27 12:08:10', '2022-09-27 12:08:10', '', 27, 'https://taeko-and-co.ch/?p=120', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
