(325, 1, '2022-12-12 19:40:09', '2022-12-12 18:40:09', '<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":1} -->\n<h1 class="has-text-align-center">A History of T&amp;C Logos</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In Taeko &amp; Co\'s two and a half years, we\'ve gone through a few iterations of logos, each time being updated to better reflect the entire project.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Every logo has been made "in house", including the latest logo, a proud product of the Grafik Dsign Club.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Taeko &amp; Co\'s Current Logo, 12th December 2022</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":317,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img src="http://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/tc_logo.png" alt="" class="wp-image-317"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Proudly produced by the GDC (Grafik Dsign Club), this logo is T&amp;C\'s trendy new look. As is a recurring theme in each design, the main drawn element is the Atami Radio Tower, a tradition since the very first logo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our name is now stylized elegantly &amp; simply "taeko&amp;co.", which is complimented by a heavy typeface, inspired by advertisements and posters of the 70\'s and 80\'s. The waves add a dynamic feeling to the logo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>November - December 2022</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":313,"width":462,"height":472,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img src="http://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/TCLOGO.png" alt="" class="wp-image-313" width="462" height="472"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The pixel-y design was conceived on the creative test server unintentionally. It looked good enough, that it was decided it should be drawn up "properly". Soon after, it replaced Taeko &amp; Co\'s aging old logo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>September 2021 - November 2022</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":270,"width":504,"height":438,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img src="http://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-02-at-11.01.34.png" alt="" class="wp-image-270" width="504" height="438"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Most of this logo is defined by new developments of the late 2021 server, namely the Atami-Atocha train station and the Lyria Tower. Additionally, an ice road was added, symbolizing the exploding expansion of ice paved roads on the server.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>November 2020 - September 2021</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":323,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/taeko_and_co_logo-1024x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-323"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Taeko &amp; Co\'s first proper logo. Intended for the planned T-Shirts of that year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>September - November 2020</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":324,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/taekotachi-1024x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-324"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Taeko &amp; Co\'s first logo, after being renamed from RMC (Retarded Minecrafters)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'A History of T&C Logos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '322-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-12-12 19:40:09', '2022-12-12 18:40:09', '', 322, 'https://taeko-and-co.ch/?p=325', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(326, 1, '2022-12-12 19:42:26', '2022-12-12 18:42:26', '<!-- wp:heading {"textAlign":"center","level":1} -->\n<h1 class="has-text-align-center">A History of T&amp;C Logos</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In Taeko &amp; Co\'s two and a half years, we\'ve gone through a few iterations of logos, each time being updated to better reflect the entire project.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Every logo has been made "in house", including the latest logo, a proud product of the Grafik Dsign Club.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Taeko &amp; Co\'s Current Logo, 12th December 2022</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":317,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img src="http://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/tc_logo.png" alt="" class="wp-image-317"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Proudly produced by the GDC (Grafik Dsign Club), this logo is T&amp;C\'s trendy new look. As is a recurring theme in each design, the main drawn element is the Atami Radio Tower, a tradition since the very first logo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our name is now stylized elegantly &amp; simply "taeko&amp;co.", which is complimented by a heavy typeface, inspired by advertisements and posters of the 70\'s and 80\'s. The waves add a dynamic feeling to the logo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>November - December 2022</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":313,"width":462,"height":472,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img src="http://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/TCLOGO.png" alt="" class="wp-image-313" width="462" height="472"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The pixel-y design was conceived on the creative test server unintentionally. It looked good enough, that it was decided it should be drawn up "properly". Soon after, it replaced Taeko &amp; Co\'s aging old logo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>September 2021 - November 2022</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":270,"width":504,"height":438,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img src="http://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screen-Shot-2022-10-02-at-11.01.34.png" alt="" class="wp-image-270" width="504" height="438"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Most of this logo is defined by new developments of the late 2021 server, namely the Atami-Atocha train station and the Lyria Tower. Additionally, an ice road was added, symbolizing the exploding expansion of ice paved roads on the server.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>November 2020 - September 2021</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":323,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/taeko_and_co_logo-1024x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-323"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Taeko &amp; Co\'s first proper logo. Intended for the planned T-Shirts of that year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>September - November 2020</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":324,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/taekotachi-1024x1024.png" alt="" class="wp-image-324"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Taeko &amp; Co\'s first logo, after being renamed from RMC (Retarded Minecrafters), intended to be temporary.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'A History of T&C Logos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '322-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-12-12 19:42:26', '2022-12-12 18:42:26', '', 322, 'https://taeko-and-co.ch/?p=326', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(328, 1, '2022-12-28 21:00:31', '2022-12-28 20:00:31', '<!-- wp:heading {"level":1} -->\n<h1>Mod Downloads for the T&amp;C Minecraft Server (1.19.2)</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Taeko &amp; Co relies on a a variety of mods to work as it does. Some mods, although not many, are required by the client. Most of these mods are simply extras, which for many of T&amp;C\'s members are essential.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ensure you have the latest version of the Fabric Mod Loader for <strong>1.19.2</strong> installed: <a href="https://fabricmc.net/use" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">https://fabricmc.net/use</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Essentials</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The following mods are required to use the server. While it may be possible to join without them, large parts of the server will not work at all or not as expected. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Create 0.5</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>T&amp;C Seasons Mod</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fabric API</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {"id":329,"href":"https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/essentials.zip"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-file"><a id="wp-block-file--media-38ae9748-63f4-4935-9189-2d303d6014f6" href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/essentials.zip">essentials</a><a href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/essentials.zip" class="wp-block-file__button wp-element-button" download aria-describedby="wp-block-file--media-38ae9748-63f4-4935-9189-2d303d6014f6">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Quality of Life</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These mods generally enhance the experience of playing the game.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Modmenu</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Litematica</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>MiniHUD</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tweakeroo</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Malilib (Libraries)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>WorldEdit (for the creative server)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {"id":330,"href":"https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/quality-of-life.zip"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-file"><a id="wp-block-file--media-a8d9fdcc-7981-42d7-9143-06bafa7eac42" href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/quality-of-life.zip">quality-of-life</a><a href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/quality-of-life.zip" class="wp-block-file__button wp-element-button" download aria-describedby="wp-block-file--media-a8d9fdcc-7981-42d7-9143-06bafa7eac42">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Performance</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These mods significantly boost performance, especially on slower computers. Don\'t skip these!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Sodium</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Phosphor</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Indium </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Spark (profiler)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {"id":331,"href":"https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/performance.zip"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-file"><a id="wp-block-file--media-5513bd51-e156-46bf-b492-bcd91789d426" href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/performance.zip">performance</a><a href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/performance.zip" class="wp-block-file__button wp-element-button" download aria-describedby="wp-block-file--media-5513bd51-e156-46bf-b492-bcd91789d426">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Necessary Extras</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These mods make Taeko &amp; Co (specifically) much better.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>TCBoatTweaker Ultra</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Xaero\'s Minimap</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Xaero\'s Worldmap</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:file {"id":332,"href":"https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/necessary-extras.zip"} -->\n<div class="wp-block-file"><a id="wp-block-file--media-8ea9b3d8-ff40-4f37-b6ce-faa94da8fe9d" href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/necessary-extras.zip">necessary-extras</a><a href="https://taeko-and-co.ch/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/necessary-extras.zip" class="wp-block-file__button wp-element-button" download aria-describedby="wp-block-file--media-8ea9b3d8-ff40-4f37-b6ce-faa94da8fe9d">Download</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:file -->', 'Mod Downloads', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mod-downloads', '', '', '2022-12-28 21:00:31', '2022-12-28 20:00:31', '', 0, 'https://taeko-and-co.ch/?p=328', 0, 'post', '', 2) ;
