ct. Here, three countries spearhead server development:<br><strong>Atteca, Lyria, and Swarovski</strong>. These countries each contain their own architecture, industry, and culture. We boast a serverwide network of roads and railway lines.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We hope to see you in our Discord or on the server soon!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class="wp-block-column"><!-- wp:html -->\n<center><iframe src="https://discord.com/widget?id=1118461204281696258&theme=dark" width="350" height="500" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" sandbox="allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts"></iframe></center>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We would love to help you with your next project with our plethora of<br>skills. For business inquiries, please visit the commisions page.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-03-18 15:52:14', '2025-03-18 14:52:14', '', 21, 'https://taeko-and-co.ch/?p=455', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
